}

docs {
  Requests a metadata cache refresh for a specific NFT token.
  Supported on Ethereum (Mainnet & Sepolia), Polygon (Mainnet, Mumbai & Amoy),
  Arbitrum One, Optimism, and Base mainnets. For other chains use getNFTMetadata
  with refreshCache: true.

  Path Parameters:
  - apiKey (string, required): Your Alchemy API key

  Body Parameters:
  - contractAddress (string, required): NFT contract address
  - tokenId (string, required): Token ID in hex or decimal format

  Returns: { status: "Queued", estimatedMsToRefresh: string }

  https://www.alchemy.com/docs/reference/nft-api-endpoints/nft-api-endpoints/nft-metadata-endpoints/refresh-nft-metadata-v-3
}
